{
  "$comment": "OpenBindings v0.2 conformance suite: operation matching cases. Each case tests the operation matching algorithm and aggregated verdict derivation. Fields: name (descriptive), target (partial OBI with optional location), candidate (partial OBI with optional roles, optional location), result (per-operation outcomes with match kind and per-slot verdicts, plus document-level verdict). Per-slot verdicts: 'aligned', 'partial', 'misaligned', 'undecidable', or 'silent' (schema absent on one or both sides). Document-level verdict: 'aligned', 'partial', 'misaligned', 'undecidable'.",
